  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EsuApi

    public class LBEsuRestApi
extends EsuRestApi
    Implements a simple load-balanced version of EsuRestApi that round-robins through a list of access point hostnames. This should increase performance in a heavily threaded environment by distributing requests against a number of hosts.
